elevator pitched when I was writing.

00:08:04.100 --> 00:08:07.730
All I wanted to do was write
a book that felt to me true,

00:08:07.730 --> 00:08:10.950
that felt like it accurately
represented what the world felt

00:08:10.950 --> 00:08:13.150
like on my nerve endings.

00:08:13.150 --> 00:08:16.730
Now I'm not a writer who
creates an elaborate plot

00:08:16.730 --> 00:08:18.830
