creating a certain feeling,

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:24.790
a certain emotional timber.

00:08:24.790 --> 00:08:27.650
And the plot usually
comes as a result of that.

00:08:27.650 --> 00:08:28.950
When I sit down to write

00:08:28.950 --> 00:08:31.800
