00:23:06.660 --> 00:23:10.290
And so I asked her to come to my
office, and she came to my office.

00:23:10.290 --> 00:23:11.590
And I was like, "Listen.

00:23:11.590 --> 00:23:12.960 position:56%
Like this paper -- Here's your paper

00:23:12.960 --> 00:23:14.260
