to be left behind.

00:25:18.320 --> 00:25:20.830
And so they kind of came
to college thinking, "Okay.

00:25:20.830 --> 00:25:23.110
I just need to get this slip
of paper and get out of here.

00:25:23.110 --> 00:25:24.410
I need to get that credential."

00:25:24.410 --> 00:25:27.650 position:56%
And then they would meet people like
