00:26:33.700 --> 00:26:37.530
the kind of big primary theme of
the book, is maternal abandonment.

00:26:37.530 --> 00:26:41.300
The main character, Faye, leaves
the other main character, Samuel,

00:26:41.300 --> 00:26:43.260
her son, when he's 11 years old.

00:26:43.260 --> 00:26:45.930
And he doesn't see her
again for about 20 years.

00:26:45.930 --> 00:26:49.410
And this has led many, many people
to ask me about my own mother.

00:26:49.410 --> 00:26:53.290
Like imagine like explaining
to like a reporter from the

00:26:53.290 --> 00:26:54.690
"New York Times" like, "No.

00:26:54.690 --> 00:26:57.040
My mom did not -- "
I've probably gone

00:26:57.040 --> 00:26:58.610
