00:27:26.760 --> 00:27:30.510
And there's this like
long pause on the phone.

00:27:30.510 --> 00:27:31.870
She sighed.

00:27:31.870 --> 00:27:34.890
She's like, "You know what
people are going to think."

00:27:34.890 --> 00:27:36.490
I'm like, "I'm sorry."

00:27:36.490 --> 00:27:39.030
So yeah. No.

00:27:39.030 --> 00:27:40.330
My mom's wonderful.

00:27:40.330 --> 00:27:45.380 position:56%
But I was never abandoned, but
